00:09:40.750 --> 00:09:42.340
Pero... bueno...

00:09:46.880 --> 00:09:47.870
¿Te pasa algo?

00:09:48.070 --> 00:09:50.320
No... solo pienso...

00:09:54.910 --> 00:09:56.540
Siento lo del pendiente.

00:09:57.120 --> 00:09:59.420
